And we are living on earth
Heat air and water (This time)

(We are reincarnated souls from that time)
And we are living on earth
Heat air and water (This time)

Nothing is new under the sun;
All has been here since time begun
With all the years we spent
(Only changing names protect the innocent)
Like seed that is planted by the water
A prayer to die before new birth
Changing its form to another
Taking on a structure just as the first

